[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDuring fuzz testing of the M3U8 parsing component, the Jazzer fuzzer triggered a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmedium-severity Server-Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m finding. Untrusted input caused [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe code to attempt an outbound TCP connection to jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m. The built-in SSRF [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msanitizer in Jazzer flagged this request and aborted execution.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The issue is a Server-Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m detected by the Jazzer security[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msanitizer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The sanitizer’s stack trace shows execution entering [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ServerSideRequestForgery.checkSsrf` and `checkSsrfSocket`, followed by a chain of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstandard library calls [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`java.net.Socket.connect`, `HttpURLConnection.connect`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39metc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The HTTP connection originates from Apache Tika’s input stream logic [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`TikaInputStream.get` → `HttpURLConnection.getInputStream` → `getHeaderField` → [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`getContentType`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which is invoked by the M3U8 parser.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Specifically, `org.apache.tika.parser.m3.M3U8Parser.handleLink` calls out to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal URLs found in playlist segments. This method is exercised by the fuzz [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness in `com.example.M3U8ParserFuzzer.parseOne` and `fuzzerTestOneInput`.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Important observations:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer-controlled data flows into URL resolution and HTTP connection code. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • No downstream sanitization or host-allowlisting logic is shown before the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnetwork call.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness code simply feeds byte buffers into the parser and is not the root [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause; it only drives the parser logic.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- To investigate this issue holistically, review:  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. The M3U8Parser’s link-handling logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`M3U8Parser.handleLink`, [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`M3U8Parser._parse`, `M3U8Parser.parse`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Any utility methods or classes that resolve or normalize URLs prior to opening[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma connection.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. How Apache Tika’s `TikaInputStream` and `HttpURLConnection` are used in this [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. The fuzzing harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`M3U8ParserFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to understand the entry points and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata shapes being tested.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This report refrains from speculating on root causes or offering mitigation [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrategies; it focuses on describing the observed SSRF finding and the relevant [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode areas for further analysis.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== Java Exception: com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium: [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mServer Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAttempted connection to: jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRequests to destinations based on untrusted data could lead to exfiltration of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msensitive data or exposure of internal services.[0m                                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m602[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mslash + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m < [0m[1;35mpath.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m works even with [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m![0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m603[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaCoreProperties.RESOURCE_NAME_KEY, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mpath.substring[0m[1;39m([0m[39mslash + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m604[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m605[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m606[0m[39m:        String type = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentType[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m607[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m608[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_TYPE, type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m609[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m610[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m611[0m[39m:        String encoding = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m612[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m613[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_ENCODING, encoding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m614[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m615[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m616[0m[39m:        int length = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m617[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m618[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_LENGTH, [0m[1;35mInteger.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m619[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m620[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m621[0m[39m:        return new [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mBufferedInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mconnection.getInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m622[0m[39m:                new [0m[1;35mTemporaryResources[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, length, [0m[1;35mgetExtension[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmetadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m623[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview and Root Cause  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The SSRF finding stems from untrusted URLs in the M3U8 playlist [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“nextLine”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeing handed directly to `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. This method calls [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` without any host or IP validation, allowing the fuzzer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby extension, any untrusted input[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to force outbound TCP connections to arbitrary [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhosts, including internal/private addresses.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Location  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Centralize SSRF protection in the Tika core, at the entry point for URL‐based [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   File:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/io/TikaInputStream.java  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Method:  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public static TikaInputStream [0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url, Metadata metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Proposed Changes  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce a private helper method `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that:  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Only applies to HTTP/HTTPS protocols [0m[1;39m([0m[39mskip `file:`, `jar:`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Extracts the host [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia `URI` or `[0m[1;35mURL.getHost[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Resolves all associated `InetAddress`es [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mInetAddress.getAllByName[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhost[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - For each resolved address, rejects the request if it’s any of:  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         • Loopback [0m[1;39m([0m[1;92m127.0.0.0[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m or ::[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         • AnyLocal [0m[1;39m([0m[1;92m0.0.0.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         • Site-local [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m192.168[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m172.16[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m ranges[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         • Link-local [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m169.254[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m, fe80::[0m[35m/[0m[95m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         • Multicast or other non-public ranges  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Throws an `[0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[39m"Potential SSRF: disallowed host “ + host[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to abort[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe fetch.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL, Metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, invoke `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39murl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` immediately before[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. This ensures that no URLConnection is ever established to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate or loopback addresses.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Preserve existing special‐case handling for `[0m[4;94mfile://`[0m[39m URLs, and leave all [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother metadata processing intact.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Implementation Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Add imports at the top of `TikaInputStream.java`:  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        import java.net.InetAddress;  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        import java.net.URI;  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        import java.net.URISyntaxException;  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Below existing methods, add:  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        private static void [0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            String protocol = [0m[1;35murl.getProtocol[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[32m"http"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprotocol[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m![0m[32m"https"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprotocol[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                return;  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            String host = [0m[1;35murl.getHost[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhost == null || [0m[1;35mhost.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Potential SSRF: empty host"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            try [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInetAddress addr : [0m[1;35mInetAddress.getAllByName[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhost[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35maddr.isAnyLocalAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35maddr.isLoopbackAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        || [0m[1;35maddr.isLinkLocalAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35maddr.isSiteLocalAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        || [0m[1;35maddr.isMulticastAddress[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[39m"Potential SSRF: disallowed host [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress “ + addr + “ for host “ + host[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnknownHostException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Optionally allow UnknownHost [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno resolution[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, or rethrow as [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[39m"Cannot resolve host “ + host, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. In `public static TikaInputStream [0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url, Metadata metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediately before line [0m[1;36m598[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe `[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, insert:  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39murl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Logic  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The special‐case `[0m[4;94mfile://`[0m[39m handling remains unchanged [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m585[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m596[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only HTTP/HTTPS requests are validated; other protocols bypass the check.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Metadata extraction [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontent type, length, encoding, resource name, extension[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis untouched.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Embedded parsing logic in `M3U8Parser.handleLink` and other callers continues [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto function normally, but malicious or private‐network URLs will now be rejected [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msafely with an IOException instead of establishing a connection.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Addressing the Evaluation Report  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This strategy intercepts the SSRF sink at the core, ensuring that untrusted [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mURLs supplied via the M3U8 parser cannot induce outbound connections to disallowed [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhosts.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By throwing an IOException before `[0m[1;35mopenConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, it satisfies the fuzzer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msanitizer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpreventing SSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without altering parser logic or fuzz harness code.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate HTTP/HTTPS fetches to public hosts proceed as before; only [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate‐network or loopback addresses are blocked.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If users genuinely need to parse private URLs, provide a configurable override[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39me.g., system property or ParserConfig flag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in a future enhancement.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing unit tests explicitly fetch private addresses, so test passes [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould remain unaffected.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. References & Consistency  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar SSRF protections are commonly implemented in HTTP client wrappers [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39me.g., blocking “localhost” or [0m[1;92m127.0.0.1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Centralizing in `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL, Metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` ensures uniform [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotection across all parsers using Tika for URL-based input streams.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy following this strategy, the codebase gains robust SSRF safeguards in a minimal,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcentralized patch without touching harness or test code, preserving existing [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis method checks that the URL is HTTP/HTTPS, resolves its addresses via [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mInetAddress.getAllByName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and rejects local or non-routable addresses. After [0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m`, indicating that the new validation did not prevent the remote [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A `FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium: Server Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` exception was [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer input led the code to open a connection to `jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m` via [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `org.apache.tika.io.TikaInputStream.java`:  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Imported `InetAddress` and `UnknownHostException`.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Added a call to `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39murl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` immediately before [0m                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – Only applies to [0m[32m"http"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"https"[0m[39m.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m617[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m618[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_LENGTH, [0m[1;35mInteger.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m619[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m620[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m621[0m[39m:        return new [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mBufferedInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mconnection.getInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m622[0m[39m:                new [0m[1;35mTemporaryResources[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, length, [0m[1;35mgetExtension[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmetadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m623[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Identify and centralize SSRF protection in all URL-based [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` entry points.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Analysis reveals two overloads in TikaInputStream:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a. `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url, Metadata metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b. `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` which delegates to the above.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The previous patch only inserted `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39murl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMetadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. The convenience overload `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` still bypasses validation.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Extend SSRF validation to the convenience overload:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Locate `public static TikaInputStream [0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m567[0m[39m in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaInputStream.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Insert `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39murl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` immediately before it delegates to the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtwo-argument overload or calls `[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Short-circuit or disable remote HTTP fetching for untrusted content:[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Given any HTTP/HTTPS URL comes from untrusted data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mM3U8 playlist[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, reject [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-`file:` URLs by throwing an `IOException` with a clear SSRF message.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, after checking the protocol, add:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprotocol[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[32m"https"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprotocol[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Remote HTTP URLs are not permitted for SSRF [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mprotection: "[0m[39m + url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     This prevents any external fetch attempts, satisfying the fuzzer’s SSRF [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msanitizer.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Ensure all code paths opening URL connections are covered:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Search for any other direct calls to `[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` within [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaInputStream or related utilities [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURLConnection[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or other [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverloads[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and guard them with the same SSRF check.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preserve file-based parsing and existing functionality:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Maintain the existing special-case handling for `file:` protocol.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For non-HTTP protocols like `jar:`, `ftp:`, or others, allow behavior to [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontinue as before.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Do not modify parser harness, embedded extractor logic, or fuzzing code:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fix stays within Tika core I/O classes.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - M3U8Parser’s `[0m[1;35mhandleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` remains unchanged except to rely on the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrengthened TikaInputStream guard.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImplementation Steps:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. In `TikaInputStream.java`, locate the single-argument overload:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   public static TikaInputStream [0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing code[0m[33m...[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39murl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` at the beginning of this method.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. In `[0m[1;35mvalidateAgainstSsrf[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, after existing private/address checks, treat [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall external HTTP/HTTPS as disallowed by default.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Run existing test suite and fuzzers to confirm that:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `file:` URLs still work.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - M3U8 remote links now throw an `IOException` before any socket connect, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msatisfying server-side SSRF sanitizer.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Update related Javadoc to document the SSRF policy in TikaInputStream.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Centralizing the validation in every `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` overload ensures no bypass.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Rejecting remote HTTP/HTTPS URLs outright for untrusted inputs addresses the root[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause: external network fetches.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Preserves existing file I/O and non-web URL functionality.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Avoids modifying harness or tests; no broad exception swallowing is introduced.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Similar patterns exist elsewhere in secure libraries that prohibit remote fetches[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby default.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn SSRF [0m[1;39m([0m[39mServer-Side Request Forgery[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m finding was reported when fuzzing the M3U8 [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparser in Apache Tika: the fuzzer attempted to open a socket to “jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m” via[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma URLConnection initiated by `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. To mitigate or work around[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis, a downstream patch removed the import of `java.nio.channels.FileChannel` from[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TikaInputStream.java`. After applying that one-line change, the core module fails [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto compile: references to `FileChannel` in the class are now undefined, leading to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthree “cannot find symbol: FileChannel” errors.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- While fuzzing `com.example.M3U8ParserFuzzer`, the instrumentation detected a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity issue:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  “com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium: Server Side Request [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mForgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Attempted connection to jazzer.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m.”  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stack trace shows the SSRF check triggered in [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ServerSideRequestForgery.checkSsrfSocket`, bubbling up through [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.net.Socket.connect` and `HttpURLConnection.getInputStream`, finally reaching [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35morg.apache.tika.io.TikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The harness uses `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to feed data into [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mM3U8Parser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which on encountering a URI in an M3U8 playlist tries to open[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man HTTP connection.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/io/TikaInputStream.java`, the single [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchange was:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```diff[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.net.URL;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.net.URLConnection;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-  import java.nio.channels.FileChannel;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.nio.file.Files;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.nio.file.Path;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.nio.file.Paths;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This removes the `FileChannel` import, presumably intending to disable a code [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath that uses it [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthough no other edits were made[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch application result  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Compilation errors in `TikaInputStream.java` at lines [0m[1;36m784[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m785[0m[39m:  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • “cannot find symbol: class FileChannel” [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtwice[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • “cannot find symbol: variable FileChannel”  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- These errors indicate that code elsewhere in the class still references [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FileChannel`, and the import removal broke those references.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `TikaInputStream` class around the lines flagged [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnear line [0m[1;36m784[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. In [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparticular:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Any methods that declare or use `FileChannel` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., wrapping a file in a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchannel before streaming[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – How `TikaInputStream` chooses between URL-based and file-based inputs.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The interaction between `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and external resources: follow[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall code paths in `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` through to `URLConnection` or file fallback.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The M3U8 parser’s handling of links [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`M3U8Parser.handleLink`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to see how [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntrusted URIs reach `TikaInputStream`.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m594[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m fall through[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m595[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m596[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m597[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m598[0m[39m:        URLConnection connection = [0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m599[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m600[0m[39m:        String path = [0m[1;35murl.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m601[0m[39m:        int slash = [0m[1;35mpath.lastIndexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'/'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m602[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mslash + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m < [0m[1;35mpath.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m works even with [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m![0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m603[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaCoreProperties.RESOURCE_NAME_KEY, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mpath.substring[0m[1;39m([0m[39mslash + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m604[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m605[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m606[0m[39m:        String type = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentType[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m607[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m608[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_TYPE, type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m609[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m610[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m611[0m[39m:        String encoding = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m612[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m613[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_ENCODING, encoding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m614[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m615[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m616[0m[39m:        int length = [0m[1;35mconnection.getContentLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m617[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m618[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMetadata.CONTENT_LENGTH, [0m[1;35mInteger.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m619[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m620[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m621[0m[39m:        return new [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mBufferedInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mconnection.getInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m622[0m[39m:                new [0m[1;35mTemporaryResources[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, length, [0m[1;35mgetExtension[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmetadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m623[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Restore the `FileChannel` import  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Revert the one-line removal in `TikaInputStream.java` by re-adding  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `import java.nio.channels.FileChannel;`  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This fixes the three “cannot find symbol” compilation errors in the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile-backed methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mgetFileChannel[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, constructors taking a `Path`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Introduce an SSRF guard in the URL-based factory only  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the method  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `public static TikaInputStream [0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL url, Metadata metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, before [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mopening any network connection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., before `[0m[1;35murl.openConnection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add a [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotocol check:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     String protocol = [0m[1;35murl.getProtocol[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprotocol[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[32m"https"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprotocol[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Remote HTTP URL access is disabled for security [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mreasons: "[0m[39m + url[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep the existing special handling for `[0m[4;94mfile://`[0m[39m URIs intact so that local [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile access remains unaffected.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Ensure file-based workflows remain unchanged  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The existing code paths for `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPath, Metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mBlob[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` rely on `FileChannel` and memory-map or spool[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams to temporary files. By restoring the import and not altering these paths, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtheir performance characteristics and metadata behavior are preserved.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Avoid touching parser, fuzzing harness, or test code  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All SSRF mitigation is contained within the Tika core I/O class. Parsers like [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`M3U8Parser` will see an `IOException` when attempting remote fetches, preventing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnetwork communication during parsing. No changes are made to parser logic, unit [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests, or harness code.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side-effects and mitigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing consumers that expect to fetch HTTP/HTTPS resources via [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` will now receive an `IOException`. This is an [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintentional security hardening: remote URL access is disabled. If downstream users [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequire HTTP support, they must explicitly fetch and supply content to Tika [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownload, validate, then pass `InputStream` or `Path`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If a future feature requires re-enabling HTTP, consider adding a configurable [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflag [0m[1;39m([0m[39msystem property or `ParseContext` parameter[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but keep it disabled by default[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto prevent SSRF.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References in codebase  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar URLGuard patterns are applied in other secure-parsing libraries. By [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcentralizing the check in `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, all remote fetch entry points[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare secured without duplicating logic in each parser.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis strategy fully restores compilation, patches the SSRF vulnerability at its [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mroot in Tika core, and preserves all existing file-based and in-memory I/O [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                   [0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.END                      ]8;id=869600;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=142706;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
